From f83f05a8df59b33ff39c8b5b60bc36553e475a0d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marco <marco@marcopolo.io>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 21:15:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 24/24] Support multiple in-process validator keymanagers and
 fix forkchoice edge cases

- Per-instance key storage in local.Keymanager to avoid global state
  collisions when multiple keymanagers run in the same process
- NewInteropKeymanagerFromIndices for arbitrary validator index lists
- ExchangeCapabilities on startup when RPC client is pre-injected
  (fixes "engine_getBlobsV2 is not supported")
- Skip proposer reorg check for genesis block (slot 0) to avoid
  "block arrived early" error from pre-genesis timestamp

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
